name: PlayStation Underground: Jampack Winter 2002
synopsis: A collection of demos from the Official PlayStation Magazine. The disc contains demos of [[The Mark of Kri]], [[Primal]], [[Ratchet & Clank]], [[Sly Cooper and the Thievius Raccoonus]], [[SOCOM: U.S. Navy SEALs]], [[Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 4]], [[Wild Arms 3]] as well as videos of [[Lara Croft Tomb Raider: The Angel of Darkness]], [[Rygar: The Legendary Adventure]].
